description: Updated 3/17/24. Thank you so much for the 300+ saves! Over 100 hours of Metal VGM instrumental covers from consoles, from NES to Switch, to indies with epic soundtracks, like Pizza Tower & Undertale. Featuring artists like Florian Haack, Megadriver, Lame Genie, Gametal, and so much more. Enjoy.
